      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DYNAMITE DOUG (4) goes very well here including four wins. Missed the frame latest (23.12) when sixth over 400m at Warragul in a Grade 5. Looks suited here and rates on top. MORAINE PIPER (7) has shown good improvement at her last two starts, hitting the frame latest when 3rd at this track over 500m. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Can measure up. CHATTER BEAST (1) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing fourth (22.57) in a Grade 5 at Ballarat. Form at the trip sound including seven wins. Goes well out of this box with a win and four minor placings. Shapes as one to consider. MIA BLONDE (2) cannot be dismissed although new to this venue.",
